### Positive number
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/double/5

### Negative number
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/double/-3

### Zero
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/double/0

### Large number
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/double/999999999

### Very large number (near max int)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/double/9999999999999999999

### Invalid input: string instead of number (expects 422)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/double/abc

### Invalid input: float instead of integer (expects 422)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/double/3.14

### Invalid input: empty parameter (expects 404)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/double/

### Invalid input: special characters (expects 422)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/double/@!#
